# Project Documentation

## 1. Introduction
Visa Application Assistant helps users understand visa procedures using chatbot interaction.

## 2. Objective
- Provide visa guidance
- Reduce confusion in visa process
- Offer step-by-step instructions

## 3. System Features
- Interactive chatbot
- Guided conversation flow
- Document information

## 4. Technologies Used
- HTML for structure
- CSS for design
- JavaScript for chatbot logic

## 5. Working Process
1. User enters query
2. Chatbot processes input
3. Chatbot provides visa information

## 6. Future Enhancements
- AI Integration
- Multi-language support
- Database connectivity
- Real visa API integration
